title: JULIAN DAVIDSON: WELCOME TO THE PRO TEAM
description: Actions speak louder than words, and with Julian Davidson this rings all too true. Julian approaches his skating like everything else in his life, with versatility and determination. Not one to steal the spotlight with fanfare or antics, as an AM Julian built a resume of video parts and interviews only comparable to contemporary pros. His approach to life off the board, with hugs and smiles for all, further drives home his professionalism. Welcome to the pro team Julian.
